window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Pulitzer Prize winner Paul Zindel delights even the most reluctant listeners with his thrilling P.C. Hawke Mysteries.</p> <p>Everyone is upset when P.C.'s junior class trip ends with classmate Timmy Warner plunging to his death over a 300-foot waterfall. So when Timmy's mom exhibits some strange behavior at the funeral, P.C. and his friend Mackenzie just have to investigate.</p> <p>What they don't expect is that the trail of clues will lead them to Los Angeles - and to a surfer who's a dead ringer for their dead classmate!</p>"; 
